@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bshviw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.82 - wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.00)))
    tmp = v2
    v2 = wp.exp(v0)
    v2 = (0.49 - v1)
    v1 = (0.86 * (v2 + wp.abs(v2 + 0.57)))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
